The 'Crimson Wasps' soon ended up in a turf war with another clan that had stolen their secrets. Rather than trying to use the skill of tongue, they used that of the weapon. Through trial and error, their shamans once again came up with a way to infuse the armor's leggings. This proved to be a major reason for their victory, as they now could carry three more insects than the enemy. 
